    "subType": "trait",
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Yomi no Koujin bloodline is from Hidden Sealed Hills, a gray and gloomy place lost somewhere between Earth and Wind Countries. This village is known to be the place where the underworld (or Yomi the realm of death) is connected to our world by a longtime ago sealed gateway. One of the gr eatest clans in this village developed centuries ago, a way to partially enter the underworld, they are known as the Ghost Clan.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Community Compendium/Yomi no Koujin Clan.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Community Compendium</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 8+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 2 from Chakra Control, Genjutsu, Hide, Intimidate, Knowledge (Ninja lore), Ninjutsu, Survival.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Advanced Bloodline (Yomi no Koujin), Chakra Affinity, Chakra Restoration, Genin, Harmony, Will over Flesh.</p><p><b>Wealth Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p>"
